``` bash
kubectl create -f master.json
```
this file is created from paddle_job.py, I also found the default image is pointing to `"typhoon1986/paddlecloud-job` which does not have `start_master` command for `paddle_k8s`, so I changed this to `paddlepaddle/paddlecloud-job` as shown above.

